{
  "text": "The PI-Wolbachia can only spread from rarity if infected females produce more infected daughters than uninfected females produce uninfected daughters (a\u03c9 >x) in which case the infection does not go to fixation but reaches an equilibrium (solid curve Figure 1A ). At equilibrium the relationship is given by [CITATION_1] :",
